# Output settings
Output demo.gif
Output demo.mp4

# Terminal settings
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

# Start
Type "samuraizer process Mar-30-at-3-30-PM.m4a"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Hide
Sleep 50ms
Show

# Show the result
Sleep 2s
Type "cat Mar-30-at-3-30-PM/summary.txt"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3s